<div class="date"> 6 Jan 2016</div>

    <p>
    If you haven&rsquo;t used <a href="http://www.gnu.org/software/emacs/manual/html_node/emacs/Imenu.html">imenu</a> in Emacs, you should try it. It gives you
    a way to select all <i>top-level items</i> of a file... functions and
    constants in source code or headers in an org-mode file.
    </p>

